            <p class="handbook-content-1 mt-4">Quang Binh province is located in the North Central region, bordering Ha Tinh to the north, Quang Tri to the south, Laos to the west and East Sea to the east. The capital of Quang Binh is Dong Hoi city, in addition there is Ba Don town and the districts of Bo Trach, Le Thuy, Minh Hoa, Quang Ninh, Quang Trach, Tuyen Hoa.</p>
            <p class="handbook-title-1 mt-3">Beautiful season</p>
            <p class="handbook-content-1 mt-2">Quang Binh's climate is divided into two distinct seasons, the rainy season from September to March of the following year, the dry season from April to August. In addition, from November to about March, the temperature in Quang Binh also decreases. fluctuates around 17-22 degrees Celsius. The best time to come here is from late March to early September.</p>
